<plot>Vijay lives with his mom, Nirmaladevi, a poor lifestyle in Bombay, India. He is unable to secure any job for himself as he has no previous experience, is unable to afford to pay a bribe for applying for a job and is dependent on his mom, who works as a Manager for a young woman's hostel. Vijay and Aarti meet, fall in love, and Aarti's dad, Daulatram, gets Vijay to work in his firm. Daulatram's boss, Vishwanath Kashyap's only son, Ajay, dislikes Vijay and gets hims fired. Daulatram then introduces Vijay to Santosh Kumar, who hires Vijay. What Vijay does not know that Santosh Kumar is an alias for Bhogilal, a man who is wanted for murder, and who is using Vijay to get even with the Kashyap family as he had been jilted by Vishwananth's wife, Lalita. This is not the only aspect of this story that Vijay is not aware of, watch what happens when Vishwanath passes away, and the secret of his first wife surfaces.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?150237</url></doc>
